<title>USA: J.C.Penney Co Inc Jan same-store sales rise.</title>
<headline>J.C.Penney Co Inc Jan same-store sales rise.</headline>
<dateline>PLANO, Texas 1997-02-06</dateline>
<text>
<p>Percent change</p>
<p>		    1997	 1996	     Total     Same-Store</p>
<p>Month	     $1,699     $1,015    + 67.4     + 13.0</p>
<p>Quarter	   $8,157     $6,632    + 23.0	+ 5.6</p>
<p>Year-to-date   $22,653    $20,562    + 10.2	+ 3.4</p>
<p>NOTE: Figures in millions except percentage.</p>
<p>    Month is   four weeks ended Jan. 25, 1997.</p>
<p>Same-store sales for each period reflect J.C. Penney stores only and do not include drug store operations. January same-store sales at its drug stores increased 11.0 percent.</p>
</text>
